sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User Browser
    participant Gateway as Data Science Gateway<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+<br/>openshift-ingress
    participant Proxy as kube-rbac-proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+<br/>service-ca cert
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant Notebook as Jupyter Notebook<br/>8888/TCP HTTP

    Note over User,Notebook: Flow 1: User Access to Notebook (with Authentication)

    User->>Gateway: GET /notebook/{ns}/{name}<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (OAuth)
    Gateway->>Proxy: Forward request<br/>TLS 1.2+ (edge termination)
    Proxy->>K8sAPI: SubjectAccessReview<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    K8sAPI-->>Proxy: Authorization Result
    alt Authorized
        Proxy->>Notebook: Forward to localhost:8888<br/>HTTP (no encryption)
        Notebook-->>Proxy: Notebook UI Response
        Proxy-->>Gateway: HTTPS Response
        Gateway-->>User: HTTPS Response
    else Unauthorized
        Proxy-->>Gateway: 403 Forbidden
        Gateway-->>User: 403 Forbidden
    end

    Note over User,Notebook: Flow 2: User Access to Notebook (without Authentication)

    User->>Gateway: GET /notebook/{ns}/{name}<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (OAuth)
    Gateway->>Notebook: Forward directly<br/>TLS terminated at Gateway
    Notebook-->>Gateway: Notebook UI Response
    Gateway-->>User: HTTPS Response

    Note over User,Notebook: Flow 3: Webhook Mutation

    participant APIServer as Kubernetes API Server<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant Webhook as ODH Notebook Controller<br/>Webhook<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS mTLS

    APIServer->>Webhook: POST /mutate-notebook-v1<br/>Auth: mTLS client cert
    Webhook->>Webhook: Check annotation<br/>inject-auth=true?
    alt inject-auth=true
        Webhook->>APIServer: Return mutated spec<br/>with kube-rbac-proxy sidecar
    else inject-auth=false
        Webhook->>APIServer: Return original spec
    end

    Note over User,Notebook: Flow 4: Controller Reconciliation

    participant Controller as Notebook Controller<br/>Manager

    Controller->>K8sAPI: Watch Notebook CRs<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    K8sAPI-->>Controller: Notebook CR Event
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create HTTPRoute<br/>in controller namespace
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create ReferenceGrant<br/>for cross-namespace access
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create NetworkPolicy<br/>in user namespace
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create Service, SA, Roles

    Note over User,Notebook: Flow 5: Data Science Pipeline Integration

    participant DSPAAPI as DSPA API<br/>8888/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+

    Controller->>K8sAPI: Watch DSPA CRs<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    K8sAPI-->>Controller: DSPA CR Event
    Controller->>DSPAAPI: Get Pipeline API Token<br/>Auth: Token from Secret
    DSPAAPI-->>Controller: API Token
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create Secret with Token<br/>in user namespace
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create RoleBinding<br/>for pipeline access
